---
interface Props {
  year: string;
  title: string;
  aboutTitle: string;
  aboutDescription: string;
  collectionsTitle: string;
  collections: string[];
}

const { 
  year, 
  title, 
  aboutTitle,
  aboutDescription,
  collectionsTitle,
  collections 
} = Astro.props;

const parsedYear = parseInt(year);
---

<section id="founded-story-section" class="py-32 lg:py-48 bg-background text-foreground">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-20 lg:gap-32">
      <div id="founded-story-left-col" class="transition-all duration-1000 opacity-0 translate-y-10">
        <div class="space-y-12">
          <div class="text-xs font-normal text-foreground/40 tracking-widest uppercase mb-8">
            Founded in {year}
          </div>
          <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-light leading-[1.1] tracking-tight text-foreground">
            {title}
          </h2>
          
          <div class="space-y-8 pt-8">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-light text-foreground tracking-tight">
              Historical Foundation
            </h3>
            <p class="text-base font-light text-foreground/70 leading-relaxed">
              Our founding vision was rooted in the belief that exceptional craftsmanship, combined with innovative thinking and unwavering commitment to quality, could transform entire industries and set new standards for excellence that would endure across generations.
            </p>
            <p class="text-base font-light text-foreground/70 leading-relaxed">
              From our earliest days, we understood that sustainable success requires more than just technical expertiseâ€”it demands a deep understanding of market dynamics, client needs, and the evolving landscape of global commerce. This holistic perspective has guided our growth and shaped our approach to every engagement.
            </p>
            <p class="text-base font-light text-foreground/70 leading-relaxed">
              Throughout our history, we have consistently invested in research, development, and the cultivation of talent, ensuring that our capabilities evolve alongside the changing needs of our clients and the broader marketplace. This commitment to continuous improvement has been instrumental in our sustained growth and market leadership.
            </p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="space-y-6 pt-8 border-t border-foreground/10">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-light text-foreground tracking-tight">
              Legacy Milestones
            </h3>
            <div class="space-y-6">
              <div class="space-y-2">
                <div class="flex items-center space-x-4">
                  <div class="text-sm font-light text-foreground/50">{year}</div>
                  <div class="w-8 h-px bg-foreground/20"></div>
                  <div class="text-sm font-light text-foreground">Company Foundation</div>
                </div>
                <p class="text-xs font-light text-foreground/60 ml-16">
                  Established with a vision to revolutionize industry standards through innovative approaches and uncompromising quality.
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="space-y-2">
                <div class="flex items-center space-x-4">
                  <div class="text-sm font-light text-foreground/50">{parsedYear + 5}</div>
                  <div class="w-8 h-px bg-foreground/20"></div>
                  <div class="text-sm font-light text-foreground">Market Expansion</div>
                </div>
                <p class="text-xs font-light text-foreground/60 ml-16">
                  Expanded operations to serve regional markets, establishing the foundation for international growth.
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="space-y-2">
                <div class="flex items-center space-x-4">
                  <div class="text-sm font-light text-foreground/50">{parsedYear + 15}</div>
                  <div class="w-8 h-px bg-foreground/20"></div>
                  <div class="text-sm font-light text-foreground">Innovation Leadership</div>
                </div>
                <p class="text-xs font-light text-foreground/60 ml-16">
                  Pioneered breakthrough methodologies that became industry standards and competitive differentiators.
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="space-y-2">
                <div class="flex items-center space-x-4">
                  <div class="text-sm font-light text-foreground/50">{parsedYear + 25}</div>
                  <div class="w-8 h-px bg-foreground/20"></div>
                  <div class="text-sm font-light text-foreground">Global Recognition</div>
                </div>
                <p class="text-xs font-light text-foreground/60 ml-16">
                  Achieved international recognition for excellence and established partnerships across multiple continents.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div id="founded-story-right-col" class="space-y-16 transition-all duration-1000 delay-200 opacity-0 translate-y-10">
        <div class="space-y-8">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-medium text-foreground tracking-wide">
            {aboutTitle}
          </h3>
          <div class="space-y-6">
            <p class="text-base font-light text-foreground/70 leading-relaxed">
              {aboutDescription}
            </p>
            <p class="text-base font-light text-foreground/70 leading-relaxed">
              Our approach combines traditional craftsmanship with cutting-edge technology, ensuring that every product and service we deliver meets the highest standards of quality and innovation. We understand that our clients depend on us not just for immediate solutions, but for long-term partnerships that drive sustainable growth and competitive advantage.
            </p>
            <p class="text-base font-light text-foreground/70 leading-relaxed">
              The depth of our expertise spans multiple disciplines and market sectors, allowing us to provide comprehensive solutions that address complex challenges from multiple perspectives. This multidisciplinary approach has consistently delivered superior outcomes for our clients and established us as a trusted advisor in our industry.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="space-y-8 pt-8 border-t border-foreground/10">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-medium text-foreground tracking-wide">
            Core Competencies
          </h3>
          <div class="space-y-6">
            <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-4">
              <div class="space-y-2">
                <div class="text-sm font-light text-foreground">Strategic Planning</div>
                <div class="text-xs font-light text-foreground/60">Long-term vision development</div>
              </div>
              <div class="space-y-2">
                <div class="text-sm font-light text-foreground">Innovation Management</div>
                <div class="text-xs font-light text-foreground/60">Technology integration</div>
              </div>
              <div class="space-y-2">
                <div class="text-sm font-light text-foreground">Quality Assurance</div>
                <div class="text-xs font-light text-foreground/60">Excellence standards</div>
              </div>
              <div class="space-y-2">
                <div class="text-sm font-light text-foreground">Market Analysis</div>
                <div class="text-xs font-light text-foreground/60">Competitive intelligence</div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="space-y-8 pt-8 border-t border-foreground/10">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-medium text-foreground tracking-wide">
            {collectionsTitle}
          </h3>
          <div class="space-y-6">
            {collections.map((collection, index) => (
              <div class="group cursor-pointer">
                <div class="flex items-start justify-between p-4 border border-foreground/10 hover:border-foreground/20 transition-colors duration-300">
                  <div class="space-y-2 flex-1">
                    <div class="text-base font-light text-foreground group-hover:text-blue-500 transition-colors duration-300">
                      {collection}
                    </div>
                    <div class="text-xs font-light text-foreground/60">
                      {index === 0 && "Comprehensive strategic consulting services designed for enterprise-level organizations seeking transformational change and sustainable competitive advantage."}
                      {index === 1 && "Specialized analytical services combining quantitative research methods with qualitative insights to deliver actionable business intelligence."}
                      {index === 2 && "Custom-tailored solutions developed specifically for unique client requirements and specialized market conditions."}
                      {index > 2 && "Detailed service offerings that address specific industry needs and market challenges through innovative methodologies and proven best practices."}
                    </div>
                  </div>
                  <div class="text-xs font-light text-foreground/40 ml-4">
                    {String(index + 1).padStart(2, '0')}
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            ))}
          </div>
          
          <div class="space-y-4 pt-6">
            <p class="text-sm font-light text-foreground/60 leading-relaxed">
              Each service category represents years of specialized development and refinement, incorporating feedback from hundreds of client engagements and continuous improvement based on emerging market trends and technological advances.
            </p>
            <p class="text-sm font-light text-foreground/60 leading-relaxed">
              Our comprehensive approach ensures that clients receive not just individual services, but integrated solutions that address their complete range of business challenges and growth objectives.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
<script is:inline>
  const section = document.getElementById('founded-story-section');
  const leftCol = document.getElementById('founded-story-left-col');
  const rightCol = document.getElementById('founded-story-right-col');

  if (section && leftCol && rightCol) {
    const observer = new IntersectionObserver((entries) => {
      entries.forEach(entry => {
        if (entry.isIntersecting) {
          leftCol.classList.remove('opacity-0', 'translate-y-10');
          leftCol.classList.add('opacity-100', 'translate-y-0');

          rightCol.classList.remove('opacity-0', 'translate-y-10');
          rightCol.classList.add('opacity-100', 'translate-y-0');
          
          observer.unobserve(section); // Stop observing after animation
        }
      });
    }, { threshold: 0.2 });

    observer.observe(section);
  }
</script>
</section>